vices/TransferServices/AreasofStudy/Documents/igetc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smc.edu%2FStudentServices%2FTransferServices%2FAreasofStudy%2FDocuments%2Figetc.pdf&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b98209f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smc.edu/StudentServices/TransferServices/AreasofStudy/Documents/igetc.pdf</a><br />\n睇返每個Area要讀d咩同讀幾多班。<br />\n<br />\n2. <a href=\"http://之後再去assist.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%8E%BBassist.org&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c0835dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">之後再去assist.org</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.assist.org/exploring-majors/browseAreas.do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.assist.org%2Fexploring-majors%2FbrowseAreas.do&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dfba5f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.assist.org/exploring-majors/browseAreas.do</a><br />\nArea of Study揀Engineering<br />\nDiscipline揀Computer Science &amp; Engineering<br />\n入面有曬UC同CSU既CS/CE major requirements<br />\n自己揀個 major再搵返SMU有咩班可以fulfill到個major requirement<br />\n跟住個list既班讀曬佢就得<br />\n<br />\n3. 屌你啦，placement test 鳩考完之後又同人讀話驚哂時間。好似英文咁，你placement test考得差要讀多個ESL。<br />\n<br />\n就黎開學都仲未reg 班，祝你好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd992a8ff5ab68dc1e817299a9d10606e3eafb0","tid":556883,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ac3e566eff1d5e2cd60e8b28504f9de309acc8","tid":556883,"uid":56751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f34b21435d6c9a75bc88743efedb512bb7280438","tid":556883,"uid":162114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T23:12:20.000Z","msg":"話說小弟就讀SMC 仲有幾日就開學<br />\n自己一條友 冇經agent 又冇fd <br />\n就咁自己飛過來讀 但好多野都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 