咁，你placement test考得差要讀多個ESL。<br />\n<br />\n就黎開學都仲未reg 班，祝你好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34909776d763ed465a87c6296d6c6a2ad45fa91","tid":556883,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"讀四堂數加一堂英其實而經好快，<br />\n當你讀cal 1,2,3 再加堂linear algebra/diff equation。再加埋eng 1個啲。基本上都無得再快/跳步。"},{"pid":"a449bf2d4936a2696af62fba092a4e97c58fe243","tid":556883,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e34909776d763ed465a87c6296d6c6a2ad45fa91","tid":556883,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"讀四堂數加一堂英其實而經好快，<br />\n當你讀cal 1,2,3 再加堂linear algebra/diff equation。再加埋eng 1個啲。基本上都無得再快/跳步。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"好多科應該唔使讀Cal 3 同埋linear algebra<br />\n但係placement test 考得差就要讀埋pre calculus D班<br />\n最盡都要由Cal 1起步"},{"pid":"4118fd5428257fb5f6ac77fec0ad010941896b2b","tid":556883,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"慢慢讀唔駛急，補著靚gpa為首要目標"},{"pid":"90cce1a4ad90a0635760e3ed1e412497aefcd28d","tid":556883,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"聽講而家transfer難過以前好多"},{"pid":"1e9e99679e14ae38e9530590f87829db1bc1356a","tid":556883,"uid":17179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話說小弟就讀SMC 仲有幾日就開學<br />\n自己一條友 冇經agent 又冇fd <br />\n就咁自己飛過來讀 但好多野都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 考完個test,  但仲未reg 科, 因為完全唔知要揀咩來讀 (想tran computer science)<br />\n   驚揀錯科哂錢哂時間, 考完個assesment test  要我讀4班數+ 1班英<br />\n    係咪跟住讀哂就OK?  但我又想考多次個test 可以讀少D 數班 (test 個陣鳩考冇溫)<br />\n    所以未揀科住    <br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n2. 有冇巴打教路點搵屋?  想同返D HK友或 大陸人住 先<br />\n    依家一條友on99 住hostel<br />\n<br />\n英文1999 講又講得差 聽又聽得一半 好多時問完office 都唔知點搞<br />\n依家好淆底 驚冇書讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又話smc 好多香港巴 但來到凈係見到大陸+日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>1. 先睇下個IGETC先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smc.edu/StudentServices/TransferServices/AreasofStudy/Documents/igetc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smc.edu%2FStudentServices%2FTransferServices%2FAreasofStudy%2FDocuments%2Figetc.pdf&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b98209f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.smc.edu/StudentServices/TransferServices/AreasofStudy/Documents/igetc.pdf</a><br />\n睇返每個Area要讀d咩同讀幾多班。<br />\n<br />\n2. 之後再去<a href=\"http://assist.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassist.org&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5d4d63d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://assist.org</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.assist.org/exploring-majors/browseAreas.do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.assist.org%2Fexploring-majors%2FbrowseAreas.do&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dfba5f3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.assist.org/exploring-majors/browseAreas.do</a><br />\nArea of Study揀Engineering<br />\nDiscipline揀Computer Science &amp; Engineering<br />\n入面有曬UC同CSU既CS/CE major requirements<br />\n自己揀個 major再搵返SMU有咩班可以fulfill到個major requirement<br />\n跟住個list既班讀曬佢就得<br />\n<br />\n3. 屌你啦，placement test 鳩考完之後又同人讀話驚哂時間。好似英文咁，你placement test考得差要讀多個ESL。<br />\n<br />\n就黎開學都仲未reg 班，祝你好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你好有心解答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我諗佢應該連咩major都未諗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾日後開學未reg班 應該咩都無 得返啲鳩屎堂同老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef49c8a14de6c557e4e487e9990e4281be6adda","tid":556883,"uid":162114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"冇車架話住邊頭好<br />\n聽講好似話 westwood 唔錯<br />\nbudget $1000到"},{"pid":"2ec073bca861809256bf46bdfea46fead743579d","tid":556883,"uid":162114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90cce1a4ad90a0635760e3ed1e412497aefcd28d","tid":556883,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"聽講而家transfer難過以前好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"巴打又係讀CC 的?<br />\n見親美國post 都有巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45839aa2e0433d22cc05d9ff1b4158708703910f","tid":556883,"uid":17179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇車架話住邊頭好<br />\n聽講好似話 westwood 唔錯<br />\nbudget $1000到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無車就住學校附近啦 如果唔係你會唔想反學"}]}